{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_10_02",
  "title": "小美山愛 2話 花火大会、盛り上げましょうね！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（あれは……愛？）\n（元気がないように見えるが……どうしたんだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Is that… Ai?）\n（She looks a bit down… I wonder what's wrong.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ、どうしようもないよね……\nこんなの、誰にも言えないよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sigh‚ there's nothing I can do about it…\nI can't tell anyone about this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "はぁー……でも……\nううん、困らせるだけだもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… but…\nNo‚ it would just cause trouble.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……愛？　どうかしたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ai? Is something wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん！？\nいえいえ、どうもしてませんよ、大丈夫です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san!?\nNo no‚ nothing's wrong‚ I'm fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6658502777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（やっぱり……愛の様子がおかしい）\n（どうして何も話してくれないんだ？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I knew it… something's off about Ai.）\n（Why won't she say anything?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（もしかして、俺が何かやらかしてしまったのか？）\n（愛の信用をなくすようなことを……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Could it be that I did something wrong?）\n（Something that made me lose Ai's trust…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……{user}さんは頼りにならないし\n莉央さん達とも、なかなか時間が合わないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… {user}-san isn't reliable‚\nand it's hard to find time with Rio-san and the others…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5589389254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "私には、相談出来る相手なんていないんだ……\nそう、私は一人……ステージでも事務所でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't have anyone I can consult with…\nThat's right‚ I'm alone… on stage‚ and even at the office…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7923199558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.2333386739
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "頼れるのは自分だけ。もう自分以外信じない……！\nうわああんっ、孤独に咲き誇れ、小美山愛！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can only rely on myself. I won't trust anyone but myself anymore…!\nWaaaah‚ bloom in solitude‚ Ai Komiyama!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ま、待ってくれ、愛！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-wait‚ Ai!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.166662852
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、急になんですか！？\nな、何か変なこと言いましたか？　私",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ what's this all of a sudden!?\nD-did I say something strange?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.5194284286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.366662852
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いや違うんだ！　……すまん、びっくりしたよな\n忙しいからこそ、小さなことでも相談してほしいなと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ no‚ that's not it! …Sorry‚ that must have surprised you.\nBecause you're busy‚ I'd like you to consult me about even small things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9596446673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "はい、もちろんです\n何かあればすぐにご相談しますよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ of course.\nI'll consult you right away if anything happens.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.7666608174
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、私一人で考えていると、考え過ぎちゃいますから\n{user}さんのこと、頼りにしてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You see‚ when I think alone‚ I tend to overthink things‚\nso I'm counting on you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、明日は花火大会の運営の方と\n打ち合わせがありますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of which‚ tomorrow we have a meeting\nwith the fireworks festival organizers‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1666732788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.5333340962
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "場所と時間と、あと打ち合わせで話す内容を\n確認したかったんですけど、今からいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanted to confirm the location‚ time‚ and\nthe content we'll discuss in the meeting. Is now okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.8666732788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。俺もそれを話そうと思っていたんだ\nじゃあ、ちょっとオフィスで話そうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. I was just about to bring that up.\nWell then‚ let's talk in the office for a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0333399455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（今回も力にはなれなかったか。でも愛の言葉に嘘は）\n（なさそうだ。本当に何かあれば相談してくれるだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I couldn't help her this time either. But there's no lie in Ai's words.）\n（If something really happens‚ she'll probably consult with me.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7666732788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 136.1833340962
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "……ふむふむ、では、明日は前の現場が終わったら\n{user}さんと一緒に移動ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hmm‚ I see. So tomorrow‚ after the previous job ends‚\nI'll be going with {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.8666732788,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 136.7666732788
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "打ち合わせ、楽しみです。沢山アイデアを提案したくて\n花火大会について改めて調べてみたんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm looking forward to the meeting. I want to propose lots of ideas‚\nso I researched the fireworks festival again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.1666732788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "今までの花火大会の映像を観てみたんですけど\n最近になるほど、花火がどんどん大輪になっていて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I watched videos of past fireworks festivals‚\nand it looks like the more recent ones have much bigger fireworks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.3445354996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "他にも、いただいた今年のプログラムだと\nキャラクターものの花火の枠が大きく増えていました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ when I looked at this year’s program‚\nthe section for character-themed fireworks has greatly increased!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.9666732788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "伝統を大切にしつつ、新しいものも取り入れていく\nMCではそこにもしっかり触れていきたいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While cherishing tradition‚ they're also incorporating new things.\nI want to properly address that in my MC work!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.8333399455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "良く調べて、しっかり意見をまとめてるな\n明日の打ち合わせで、きっと先方も喜んでくれるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've researched well and organized your opinions properly.\nI'm sure the other party will be pleased at tomorrow's meeting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.5000066121,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
