      "text": "調べたら調べるだけ、詰め込みたいことが出てきて……\n昨日も徹夜したんですけど、全然足りないんですよぉ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The more I research‚ the more ideas I want to include…\nI pulled an all-nighter yesterday‚ but it's not nearly enough!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.9730475425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_02-ai020.m4a",
      "text": "本番までには！　本番までには絶対に！\n最高のステージにしてみせますから！　それでは！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Before the performance! I swear‚ before the performance!\nI'll make it the best stage! Well then!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.2333399455,
      "sfxList": [
